name: Gardens of Atlantis
description:
The Gardens of Atlantis are a magical fantasy world. The Gardens have an elaborate system that controls the weather and climate in the Gardens. The gardens are also home to many different species of plants, animals, and insects.

The Queen of Atlantis is a powerful woman who rules over all that goes on in the Gardens. She is often seen walking through her domain with her loyal guard at her side or sitting on her throne overlooking all that happens in her realm.
